<div id="carouselslide-67f1d82d08-slide" class="rad-carousel-image-and-text__slide-text">
	<h4 class="rad-carousel-image-and-text__slide-title">KION：AIロボットPhysical AIを活用した倉庫自動化</h4>
	<p class="rad-carousel-image-and-text__slide-body">AIを用いたシミュレーションで学習したヒューマノイドロボットがヒトと協働し、コストとリスクを削減しながら、倉庫業務の安全性とイノベーション向上を実現しています。</p>
	<a href="/jp-ja/case-studies/technology/ai-robots-transforming-warehouses" target="_self" data-barba-transition aria-label="続きを読む: KION：AIロボットPhysical AIを活用した倉庫自動化" data-cmp-data-layer="{&#34;carouselslide-67f1d82d08-cta&#34;:{&#34;@type&#34;:&#34;cio-sites/components/rad/modules/carouselslide&#34;,&#34;xdm:linkURL&#34;:&#34;/jp-ja/case-studies/technology/ai-robots-transforming-warehouses&#34;,&#34;analytics-engagement&#34;:&#34;true&#34;,&#34;analytics-link-type&#34;:&#34;engagement&#34;,&#34;analytics-link-name&#34;:&#34;続きを読む: KION：AIロボットPhysical AIを活用した倉庫自動化&#34;,&#34;analytics-module-name&#34;:&#34;client story card button&#34;}}" data-cmp-clickable="" class="rad-carousel-image-and-text__slide-cta rad-button rad-button--tertiary">
		<div class="rad-button__text">続きを読む</div>
		<div class="rad-button__icon-right rad-icon rad-icon__chevron-right rad-icon--compact"></div>
	</a>
</div>

    
</div>
<div class="rad-carousel-image-and-text__slide" role="group" aria-roledescription="slide"><div id="carouselslide-6efc595bd0" data-cmp-data-layer="{&#34;carouselslide-6efc595bd0&#34;:{&#34;@type&#34;:&#34;cio-sites/components/rad/modules/carouselslide&#34;,&#34;analytics-module-name&#34;:&#34;carouselslide-2&#34;,&#34;analytics-template-zone&#34;:&#34;body&#34;}}" class="cmp-image">
	
		<img class="cmp-image__image" data-flickity-lazyload="https://dynamicmedia.accenture.com/is/image/accenture/Accenture-Sustainability-Feeding-The-World%3Arad-3x2?ts=1721906660096&amp;fit=constrain&amp;dpr=off" alt/>
	
	
</div>
<div id="carouselslide-6efc595bd0-slide" class="rad-carousel-image-and-text__slide-text">
	<h4 class="rad-carousel-image-and-text__slide-title"> 世界に持続可能な食料供給を</h4>
	<p class="rad-carousel-image-and-text__slide-body">世界の食料システムは未だ「持続不可能」な道を歩んでいます。グッドフードインスティテュート（GFI）とアクセンチュアは、食肉代替イノベーションを加速し、世界的な普及拡大を目指しています。</p>
	<a href="/jp-ja/case-studies/consumer-goods-services/meat-alternative-innovation" target="_self" data-barba-transition aria-label=" 続きを読む:  世界に持続可能な食料供給を" data-cmp-data-layer="{&#34;carouselslide-6efc595bd0-cta&#34;:{&#34;@type&#34;:&#34;cio-sites/components/rad/modules/carouselslide&#34;,&#34;xdm:linkURL&#34;:&#34;/jp-ja/case-studies/consumer-goods-services/meat-alternative-innovation&#34;,&#34;analytics-engagement&#34;:&#34;true&#34;,&#34;analytics-link-type&#34;:&#34;engagement&#34;,&#34;analytics-link-name&#34;:&#34; 続きを読む:  世界に持続可能な食料供給を&#34;,&#34;analytics-module-name&#34;:&#34;client story card button&#34;}}" data-cmp-clickable="" class="rad-carousel-image-and-text__slide-cta rad-button rad-button--tertiary">
		<div class="rad-button__text"> 続きを読む</div>
		<div class="rad-button__icon-right rad-icon rad-icon__chevron-right rad-icon--compact"></div>
	</a>
</div>

    
</div>
<div class="rad-carousel-image-and-text__slide" role="group" aria-roledescription="slide"><div id="carouselslide-7e7c76ec1b" data-cmp-data-layer="{&#34;carouselslide-7e7c76ec1b&#34;:{&#34;@type&#34;:&#34;cio-sites/components/rad/modules/carouselslide&#34;,&#34;analytics-module-name&#34;:&#34;carouselslide-3&#34;,&#34;analytics-template-zone&#34;:&#34;body&#34;}}" class="cmp-image">
	
